            "required": false,
            "helpText": "Optional server/transport args. Supports --url/--base-url/--address and --api-key."
          }
        ]
      },
      "notes": ["vLLM exposes an OpenAI-compatible server and official model discovery via /models.", "llama.cpp server exposes an OpenAI-compatible chat completions endpoint; model discovery varies by server build."],
      "capabilities": {
